  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gst FFMpeg</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Gst FFMpeg</application> contains GStreamer plugins
      for <application>FFMpeg</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

    &gst-compat;

