  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of Gst FFMpeg</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Gst FFMpeg</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../gst-ffmpeg-&gst-ffmpeg-version;-gcc-4.7-1.patch &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --with-package-name="GStreamer FFMpeg Plugins &gst-ffmpeg-version; BLFS" \
            --with-package-origin="http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/&blfs-version;/" &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, issue: <command>make check</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

